[TooltipLink dataFor:"determinanty"][HeaderWithInfo tag:"h1"]Determinanty[/HeaderWithInfo][/TooltipLink]

[ReactTooltip id:"determinanty" className:"tooltipWhiteBig"]
Nech [Equation]n \in \mathbb{N}[/Equation] a nech [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] je štvorcová matica [Equation]n[/Equation]-tého rádu. Determinantom matice [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] nazývame číslo [Equation]\det{(\mathbf{A})}[/Equation], pre ktoré platí:

[CustomTable className:"center-equation-by-equal-sign" style:`{ maxWidth: "700px", fontSize: "15px"}`]
  [tbody]
    [tr]
      [td style:`{ paddingRight: "10px" }`]1. [/td]
      [td className:"text-left"]
        [equation className:"text-left" style:`{ paddingRight: "10px"}`]
          \det{(\mathbf{A})} = a_{11},
        [/equation] pre [Equation]n=1[/Equation],
      [/td]
    [/tr]
    [tr]
      [td style:`{ paddingRight: "10px" }`]2. [/td]
      [td className:"text-left" style:`{ textAlign: "left"}`]
        [equation className:"text-left" style:`{ paddingRight: "10px"}`]
          \det{(\mathbf{A})} = a_{11} \det {(\mathbf{M}_{11})} - a_{12} \det {(\mathbf{M}_{12})} + \ldots + (-1)^{1+n} a_{1n} \det {(\mathbf{M}_{1n})},
        [/equation] pre [Equation]n\geq2[/Equation],
      [/td]
    [/tr]
  [/tbody]
[/CustomTable]

kde [Equation]\mathbf{M}_{ij}[/Equation] je  matica rádu [Equation](n-1)[/Equation], ktorá vznikne z matice [Equation]\mathbf{A}[/Equation] vynechaním [Equation]i[/Equation]-tého riadku a [Equation]j[/Equation]-tého stĺpca.
[/ReactTooltip]

